Transmission Customers:

Transmission Service Offerings are being posted for the month of March 2002
to the AP OASIS on January 31, 2002.  The upload will include ATC's for all
valid AP paths (AEP, PJM, VAP, FE and DLCO).

				*	Yearly service that was not given
the option to exercise roll-over rights on the PJM paths (AP to PJM and PJM
to AP) will be given the option to extend that service through the month of
March.  AP will attempt to call these Transmission Customers by 6:30 p.m.
EST on January 31, 2002.

				*	Transmission Marketing will post a
message on the OASIS when the ATC upload is started and when it is complete.

*	The deadline for reserving March Monthly Transmission Service is
14:00 on February 28, 2002.

				*	Transmission service beyond April 1,
2002, will continue to be sold by PJM per the Interim Coordination Agreement
that was filed with FERC on February 12, 2001.


If you have any additional questions or concerns, please call Transmission
Marketing at (724) 838-6064.
